<lb n="0875a20"/>休多大多禰<note place="inline">二十二</note>闍波底<note place="inline">三十三</note><note n="0875022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哆嫟＝嫟哆【三】【甲】</note><note n="0875022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哆嫟＝嫟哆【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0875022"><lem>哆嫟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">嫟哆</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0875023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">微＝徵【元】【明】</note><app n="0875023"><lem>微</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">徵</rdg></app>耶<note n="0875024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝切【明】，〔反〕－【甲】</note><app n="0875024"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">切</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>沙摩
<lb n="0875a21"/>&CB00540;<note n="0875025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔吳音反〕－【明】</note><app n="0875025"><lem><note place="inline">吳音<note n="0875026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔反〕－【元】</note><app n="0875026"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>知<note place="inline"><anchor id="fxT21p0875a04"/>胝迤反二十四</note><note n="0875027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（知脛迤反）＋蜀【宋】，（知同上）＋蜀【元】【明】，（知脛迤）＋蜀【甲】</note><app n="0875027"><lem>蜀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">知脛迤反蜀</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">知同上蜀</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">知脛迤蜀</rdg></app>伽羅婆底<note place="inline">二十五</note>陟沙
<lb n="0875a22"/>拏佛朕<note place="inline">持引<anchor id="fxT21p0875a05"/>反</note>地<note n="0875028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝邪【三】</note><note n="0875028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶＝邪【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0875028"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">邪</rdg></app>佛地<note n="0875029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瑣＝莎【甲】</note><app n="0875029"><lem>瑣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">莎</rdg></app>訶<note place="inline"><note n="0875030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝熙荷反【宋】【甲】，同上【元】【明】</note><note n="0875030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引＝熙荷反【宋】【甲】，＝同上【元】【明】</note><app n="0875030"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【甲】" resp="Taisho">熙荷反</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">同上</rdg></app>二十六</note></p><p type="inline">師子威
<lb n="0875a23"/>當知。若善男子能於此華積神&CB00057;。若讀若誦。
<lb n="0875a24"/>是人當於三月四月九月。從八日至十五日。
<lb n="0875a25"/>一心憶念如來相好。夜中三誦華積神&CB00057;。日中
<lb n="0875a26"/>亦三。至月圓時。當以<note n="0875031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香華＝華香【三】【甲】</note><note n="0875031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香華＝華香【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0875031"><lem>香華</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">華香</rdg></app>燈燭於形像前而
<lb n="0875a27"/>修供養。并誦華積陀羅尼&CB00057;。其人是夜夢見
<lb n="0875a28"/>如來。相好具足坐蓮華座為眾說法。亦得華
<lb n="0875a29"/>積陀羅尼&CB00057;。於現世中常得強記。智慧深信。
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1356.0875b" n="0875b"/>
<lb n="0875b01"/>從今身乃至涅槃。常一聞持一切聞見。一切
<lb n="0875b02"/>經教一切學解。一切<note n="0875032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">技＝伎【宋】</note><app n="0875032"><lem>技</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">伎</rdg></app>藝通達無礙。於一切
<lb n="0875b03"/>三昧深得清淨。解四聖諦無上法輪。說是經
<lb n="0875b04"/>已。師子威等天龍八部。一切大眾歡喜奉行</p>
